(1500, 385, '_tour_schedule_info', '<div class="panel-heading">\n<h4 class="panel-title">Day 1</h4>\n</div>\n<div class="panel-collapse in collapse">\n<div class="panel-body">\n<div class="ng-binding ng-scope">\n<p>Journey start from Dhaka ….overnight journey.Arrive Rangamati 07.30 &amp; transfer to hotel. After breakfast start for visit (5 point) sightseeing (Shovolong,Peda ting ting, Raj Bari, Bona Bihar &amp; Hanging Bridge Evening free. On Over-night at Rangamati.</p>\n<div class="panel-heading">\n<h4 class="panel-title"><span class="ng-binding">Day 2</span></h4>\n</div>\n<div class="panel-collapse in collapse">\n<div class="panel-body">\n<div class="ng-binding ng-scope">\n<p>Leave Rangamati for Bandarban at 07.30. (In side road, 0330 journey). After arrive Journey start for visit-Chimbuk top hill &amp; back way enjoy Shailo Propat, Nilachal then evening visit Golden Temple. Meghla by Jeep. On Over-night at Bandarban.</p>\n<div class="panel-heading">\n<h4 class="panel-title"><span class="ng-binding">Day 3</span></h4>\n</div>\n<div class="panel-collapse in collapse">\n<div class="panel-body">\n<div class="ng-binding ng-scope">\n<p>Breakfast. Journey start for Dhaka.Arrival Dhaka at morning.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n'),
