(2112, 450, '_tour_schedule_info', '<p>Day 01 : Dhaka–Kathmandu-Nagorkot :</p>\n<p>Departure for Dhaka at 1220hrs by Bangladesh Biman<br />\nArrival at 1330hrs, Meet &amp; greets with our local guide<br />\nTransfer to Nagorkot hotel, enjoy sunset &amp; overnight at hotel</p>\n<p>Day 02 : Nagorkot-Kathmandu :</p>\n<p>After breakfast Checkout from Hothttp://ghuri.online/wp-admin/post.php?post=450&amp;action=editel<br />\nStart Journey Kathmandu<br />\nArrive Kathmandu &amp; transfer to hotel<br />\nOvernight stay</p>\n<p>Day 03 : Kathmandu :</p>\n<p>Breakfast at hotel<br />\nEnjoy half day sightseeing<br />\nOvernight stay</p>\n<p>Day 04 : Kathmandu-Dhaka :</p>\n<p>After breakfast free time.<br />\nCheckout and transfer to Airport<br />\nDepart for Dhaka at 1610hrs<br />\nArrive Dhaka at 1740hrs &amp; End the Trip</p>\n<p>Flight Schedule :</p>\n<p>Daily</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Terms and Conditions</strong></p>\n<div id="Conditions">\n<ul>\n<li>Cost based on Twin sharing Per person</li>\n<li>Extra Person / Child with Bed (CWB) sharing the Room on mattress.</li>\n<li>All Transfer &amp; Sightseeing will be done as per the vehicle details mentioned</li>\n<li>Children above 10+ years will be charged 100% as per Adult Rate</li>\n<li>Children of 5+ to 10 sharing parent’s room will be charged 75% as per child no bed (CNB).</li>\n<li>Children below 5 years charge only Airfare &amp; visa fees.</li>\n<li>Hotels are very strict with the child policy. Please carry the age proof so that it can be produced when asked for</li>\n<li>Plan as per the details mentioned in the Itinerary.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n'),
