(4846, 924, '_tour_schedule_info', '<p><strong>Detailed Itinerary </strong></p>\n<p><strong>Day 1</strong></p>\n<p>Welcome to London! On arrival at Heathrow International Airport make your way a cab to your hotel. Following check-in, enjoy your day at leisure. Overnight: Park Inn by Radisson London Heathrow.</p>\n<p><strong>Day 2</strong></p>\n<p>Following Breakfast, enjoy your day exploring London. In the afternoon, enjoy complimentary afternoon tea at the hotel. In the evening, enjoy a 3 course dinner in the famous Indian Restaurant. Consider seeing: Changing of the Guards at Buckingham Palace, shopping at Harrods, or explore historical and contemporary art and design at the Victoria and Albert Museum. Overnight: Park Inn by Radisson London Heathrow</p>\n<p><strong>Day 3</strong></p>\n<p>Following Breakfast, enjoy your day exploring London. In the afternoon, enjoy complimentary afternoon tea at the hotel. Consider seeing: Tower of London, St. Paul''s Cathedral, a ride on the London Eye, or take in modern art at Tate Modern, Big Ben, Westminster Abbey and more. Overnight: Park Inn by Radisson London Heathrow</p>\n<p><strong>Day 4</strong></p>\n<p>Following Breakfast, enjoy your day exploring London. In the afternoon, enjoy complimentary afternoon tea at the hotel. Consider seeing: Trafalgar Square, seeing the greatest collections of European painting at the National Gallery, Thames river, Madame Tussauds or shop and stroll down Oxford Street. Overnight: Park Inn by Radisson London Heathrow</p>\n<p><strong>Day 5</strong></p>\n<p>Following Breakfast, enjoy your day exploring London. In the afternoon, enjoy complimentary afternoon tea at the hotel. Consider travelling outside the city to Stonehenge, Warner Bros. Studio Tour London for a Harry Potter studio tour, or the famous Universities of Oxford or Cambridge. Overnight: Park Inn by Radisson London Heathrow</p>\n<p><strong>Day 6</strong></p>\n<p>Following Breakfast, take the Heathrow back to the Airport for your departure flight home.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Package Includes:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Return Air Tickets including all taxes</li>\n<li>Stay at a 4 Star Hotel with breakfast (Twin Share basis) &amp; Buffet dinner at Indian Restaurant</li>\n<li>Transport services for all the sight viewing.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Package Excludes :</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Service charge per person BDT 15,000</li>\n<li>Visa Assistance Fees Applicable</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Terms and Conditions</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Cost based on Twin sharing Per person</li>\n<li>Extra Person / Child with Bed (CWB) sharing the Room on mattress.</li>\n<li>All Transfer &amp; Sightseeing will be done as per the vehicle details mentioned</li>\n<li>Children above 10+ years will be charged 100% as per Adult Rate</li>\n<li>Children of 5+ to 10 sharing parent’s room will be charged 75% as per child no bed (CNB).</li>\n<li>Children below 5 years charge only Airfare &amp; visa fees.</li>\n<li>Hotels are very strict with the child policy. Please carry the age proof so that it can be produced when asked for</li>\n<li>Plan as per the details mentioned in the Itinerary.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n'),
