(688, 1, '2016-07-05 16:58:29', '2016-07-05 10:58:29', 'Swiss Valley is a cozy, eco-friendly, leisure and activity resort located on small hill or tila next to the Shamsher Nagar Airport and Shamsher Nagar Tea garden of Duncan Brothers.\r\n\r\nWe do offer 5 different sizes separated cottages with 9 rooms and dining area- each of them has own lucrative designs. Specifically interiors and exteriors made by the wood and bamboo with all other modern amenities. Resort got swimming pool separated with kids and adult pools. All of our structures have been crafted by hand using natural and local materials. All the construction work at Swiss Valley has been done by the local people thus providing employment and socially responsible tourism.\r\n\r\nAt Swiss Valley we love adventure and nature and our guests can relax on easy chairs, bamboo house around the resort with a book in their hand in the calm and noise-free zone and sit-outs. Children can run around, swim in the pool or play football, badminton and other sports on the ground and enjoy looking at the dragonflies, butterflies, fireflies, birds around the resort.\r\n\r\nFishing is going to add with our facilities soon to provide an extra advantage to pass leisure pleasantly.\r\n\r\nImportantly two different type of Tribal’s own paradise known as Kashaya and Monipuri are living closely with their unique livelihood. Moreover, Lawachora National ECO park, adventure in deep forest (Adompur bit), ham-ham waterfall, Baikkar bill, Hakaluki hawor, tallest waterfall of our country Madhobkunda located around of the Moulvibazar.\r\n\r\nFor experiencing real natural beauty, different culture oriented group of people and a proper adventure you should choose Swiss Valley.\r\n\r\nWe look forward to seeing you at Swiss Valley Resort.', 'Swiss Valley Resort', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'swiss-valley-resort', '', '', '2016-07-21 20:33:31', '2016-07-21 14:33:31', '', 0, 'http://ghuri.online/?post_type=hotel&#038;p=688', 0, 'hotel', '', 0),
