(735, 1, '2016-07-15 22:26:53', '2016-07-15 16:26:53', '<span id="one:_t136" class="black_light1">The city stands at an elevation of approximately 1,400 metres (4,600 ft) in the bowl-shaped Kathmandu Valley of central Nepal.It is surrounded by four major mountains: Shivapuri, Phulchoki, Nagarjun, and Chandragiri. Kathmandu Valley is part of three districts (Kathmandu, Lalitpur, and Bhaktapur), has the highest population density in the country</span>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong>Package Includes :</strong>\n\nReturn Air tickets of Bangladesh Biman (BG)\nAirport-Nagorkot hotel-Kathmandu hotel-Airport transfer (SIC)\n01 night double sharing accommodation at Nagorkot Hotel Bhangeri Durbar Resort / Paradise Inn 3* or similar hotel\n02 nights double sharing accommodation at Kathmandu Hotel Marshyangdi 3* or Similar Hotel\nHalf day city tour at Kathmandu\n\n<strong>Package Excludes :</strong>\n\nLunch, Dinner\nWhich is not mention in includes\n\n<span class="h5"><strong>Hotel Information:</strong></span>\n<table cellpadding="10px">\n<tbody>\n<tr valign="top">\n<td valign="top"><span class="h5"><span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:_t228">Hotel Space Mountain / Similar</span></span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr valign="top">\n<td valign="top"><span class="h5">Star Rating:</span> <img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/staticResources/filled_star.jpg" alt="" width="18" height="18" /> <img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/staticResources/filled_star.jpg" alt="" width="18" height="18" /> <img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/staticResources/filled_star.jpg" alt="" width="18" height="18" /></td>\n</tr>\n<tr valign="top">\n<td valign="top">\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td valign="top"><span class="h5"> Address:</span></td>\n<td><span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt233:0:_t235" class="black_light1">Hotel Space Mountain</span><span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt233:0:_t238" class="black_light1">, Nagorkot</span><span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt233:0:_t239" class="black_light1">, Nepal</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr valign="top">\n<td valign="top">&nbsp;\n\n<span class="h5"><strong>Hotel Description:</strong> </span>\n<span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:_t243" class="black_light1">Offers 34 cosy rooms with attached bathroom and private balcony overlooking Kathmandu valley in a distance quarantines impressive sunrise and sunset views every morning and evening. The guest rooms also features multichannel TV, Intl’ telephone access &amp; WI-FI internet service.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr valign="top">\n<td valign="top"><span class="h5">Features Characteristics:</span>\n•      <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:0:_t247" class="black_light1">Bar/Lounge.</span>\n•      <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:1:_t247" class="black_light1">Business Centre.</span>\n•      <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:2:_t247" class="black_light1">Car parking.</span>\n•      <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:3:_t247" class="black_light1">Doctor on call.</span>\n•      <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:4:_t247" class="black_light1">Restaurant.</span>\n•      <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:5:_t247" class="black_light1">Room service.</span>\n•      <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:6:_t247" class="black_light1">Hot / cold water.</span><strong>About Destination:</strong>\n\n<img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/70mmtours/images/int_destination/bhaktapur1.jpg" alt="" />\n\n<strong><span class="h5"><span id="one:j_idt311:1:j_idt313:5:_t317">Bhaktapur Nagorkot</span></span></strong>\n\n<span id="one:j_idt311:1:j_idt313:5:_t319" class="black_light1">Bhaktapur is known variously as City of Culture, Living Heritage, Nepal''s Cultural Gem, An open museum and a City of Devotees. Bhaktapur is an ancient city and is renowned for its elegant art, fabulous culture, colorful festivals, traditional dances and indigenous lifestyle of Newari community. It is just 12 kilometers east of Kathmandu, capital of Nepal, but gives the feeling of prehistoric times given the ambiance of traditional homes, lifestyles and environment. The conch shaped historic city is spreading over just an area of 6.88 square kilometer at 1,401 meter altitude.</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>', 'Kathmandu & Nagorkot ( 04 Days 03 Nights )', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '450-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-07-15 22:26:53', '2016-07-15 16:26:53', '', 450, 'http://ghuri.online/450-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(736, 1, '2016-07-15 22:26:08', '2016-07-15 16:26:08', '<span id="one:_t136" class="black_light1">Kuala Lumpur is the capital of Malaysia. Over 8 million people live within the greater Kuala Lumpur area which is clearly noticeable by the huge and vast amounts of traffic that goes into the city every morning, and slowly leaves the city in the evening. Kuala Lumpur has many interesting attractions; like Merdeka Square, Chinatown, Petronas Twin Towers and much more.</span>\r\n\r\n<strong>Package Includes :</strong>\r\n\r\n• Return Air tickets by Malindo Air with taxes\r\n• Airport - Hotel - Airport transfer (SIC)\r\n• 02 nights double sharing accommodation at Kuala Lumpur Hotel Sentral Pudu, Sky Express &amp; Soleil 3* or Similar Hotel\r\n• 01 half day City tour at Kuala Lumpur\r\n\r\n<strong>Package Excludes :</strong>\r\n\r\n•     Visa Fees &amp; service charge per person BDT 4,500/-\r\n•     Lunch, Dinner\r\n•     Which is not mention in includes\r\n\r\n<strong>Hotel Information:</strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/70mmtours/images/in_hotel/arenaa_star.jpg" alt="" width="183" height="124" />\r\n<table cellpadding="10px">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr valign="top">\r\n<td valign="top"><strong><span class="h5"><span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:_t228">Hotel Sentral Pudu / Sky Express / Soleil or Similar</span></span></strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr valign="top">\r\n<td valign="top"><span class="h5">Star Rating:</span> <img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/staticResources/filled_star.jpg" alt="" width="18" height="18" /> <img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/staticResources/filled_star.jpg" alt="" width="18" height="18" /> <img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/staticResources/filled_star.jpg" alt="" width="18" height="18" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr valign="top">\r\n<td valign="top">\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top"><span class="h5"> Address:</span></td>\r\n<td><span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt233:0:_t235" class="