(739, 1, '2016-07-15 22:59:20', '2016-07-15 16:59:20', '<span id="one:_t136" class="black_light1">Bangkok is the capital and the most populous city of Thailand. It is known in Thai as Krung Thep Maha Nakhon or simply About this sound Krung Thep. The city occupies 1,568.7 square kilometres (605.7 sq mi) in the Chao Phraya River delta in Central Thailand, and has a population of over 8 million, or 12.6 percent of the country''s population</span>\r\n\r\n<strong>Package Includes :</strong>\r\n\r\n•     Return Air Tickets by Regent Airways with all taxes.\r\n•     Airport-Hotel-Airport transfer (SIC)\r\n•     02 nights double sharing accommodation at Hotel Hotel Ambassador or Unico Express Hotel 3* or Similar Hotel , Bangkok\r\n•     Breakfast at hotel\r\n•     Enjoy full day Safari world &amp; Marine Park with lunch.\r\n\r\n<strong>Package Excludes :</strong>\r\n\r\n•     Visa Fees &amp; service charge per person BDT 4,500/-\r\n•     Lunch, Dinner\r\n•     Which is not mention in includes\r\n\r\n<strong>Hotel Information:</strong>\r\n\r\n<img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/70mmtours/images/in_hotel/unico_express.jpg" alt="" width="100" height="100" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<table cellpadding="10px">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr valign="top">\r\n<td valign="top"><span class="h5"><span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:_t228">Hotel Unico Express / Similar</span></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr valign="top">\r\n<td valign="top"><span class="h5">Star Rating:</span> <img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/staticResources/filled_star.jpg" alt="" width="18" height="18" /> <img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/staticResources/filled_star.jpg" alt="" width="18" height="18" /> <img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/staticResources/filled_star.jpg" alt="" width="18" height="18" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr valign="top">\r\n<td valign="top">\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top"><span class="h5"> Address:</span></td>\r\n<td><span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt233:0:_t235" class="black_light1">Hotel Unico Express</span><span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt233:0:_t238" class="black_light1">, Bangkok</span><span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt233:0:_t239" class="black_light1">, Thailand</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr valign="top">\r\n<td valign="top"><span class="h5"> Hotel Description: </span>\r\n<span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:_t243" class="black_light1">The Unico group is pleased to be able to introduce The Unico Express Sukhumvit, situated in the heart of Bangkok with easy access to a wealth of amenities and some of the most specular sights Thailand has to offer. This property offers excellent value for money to price conscience guests with a transparent pricing scheme that is affordable for all. Within easy walking distance of Bangkok’s famous Bumrungrad Hospital, the Unico Express is ideally situated for friends and family of patients as well as those looking to recuperate.</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr valign="top">\r\n<td valign="top"><span class="h5">Features Characteristics:</span>\r\n• <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:0:_t247" class="black_light1">Bar/Lounge.</span>\r\n• <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:1:_t247" class="black_light1">Business Centre.</span>\r\n• <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:2:_t247" class="black_light1">Car parking.</span>\r\n• <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:3:_t247" class="black_light1">Doctor on call.</span>\r\n• <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:4:_t247" class="black_light1">Restaurant.</span>\r\n• <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:5:_t247" class="black_light1">Room service.</span>\r\n• <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:6:_t247" class="black_light1">Hot / cold water.</span><strong>About Destination:</strong><img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/70mmtours/images/int_destination/safari_park3.jpg" alt="" /><strong><span class="h5"><span id="one:j_idt311:1:j_idt313:5:_t317">Safari Park</span></span></strong>\r\n\r\n<span id="one:j_idt311:1:j_idt313:5:_t319" class="black_light1">Safari World is a sight seeing in Bangkok, Thailand that consists of two parks named Marine Park and Safari Park, operated by Safari World Public Limited. The park was opened in 1988 with a total area of 480 acres (190 ha) for its open zoo and 180 acres (73 ha) for its bird park</span>\r\n\r\n<img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/70mmtours/images/int_destination/ocean_world1.jpg" alt="" />\r\n\r\n<strong><span class="h5"><span id="one:j_idt311:1:j_idt313:6:_t317">Ocean World</span></span> </strong>\r\n\r\n<span id="one:j_idt311:1:j_idt313:6:_t319" class="black_light1">The Sea Life Bangkok Ocean World Bangkok aims to provide both entertainment and education to visitors. Through formal educational programs, the aquarium aims to promote an appreciation and understanding of the aquatic environment in line with the formal Thailand curriculum</span>\r\n\r\n<img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/70mmtours/images/int_destination/dinner_cruise3.jpg" alt="" />\r\n\r\n<span id="one:j_idt311:1:j_idt313:17:_t319" class="black_light1">Siam Niramit is a grandiose tour through Thai culture and history taking its audience back in time to mystical bygone eras. Quite rightly billed as a ‘World Class Spectacular Show’, this captivating 80-minute journey uncovers the history, customs and cultural treasures that have descended through centuries and which continue to fascinate Thailand’s visitors</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', 'Bangkok Tour, Thailand (3 Days 2 Nights)', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'bangkok-tour-thailand-3-days-2-nights', '', '', '2016-08-02 17:25:06', '2016-08-02 11:25:06', '', 0, 'http://ghuri.online/?post_type=tour&#038;p=739', 0, 'tour', '', 0),
