(749, 1, '2016-07-24 16:16:33', '2016-07-24 10:16:33', '<span id="one:_t136" class="black_light1">Singapore officially the Republic of Singapore, is a modern city-state and island country in Southeast Asia. It lies off the southern tip of the Malay Peninsula and is 137 kilometres (85 mi) north of the equator. The country''s territory consists of the diamond-shaped main island, commonly referred to as Singapore Island in English and Pulau Ujong in Malay, and more than 60 significantly smaller islets.</span>\n\n<strong>Package Includes :</strong>\n\n•     Return Air tickets by Regent Airways with taxes\n•     Airport-Hotel-Airport transfer (SIC)\n•     02 Nights double sharing accommodation at Hotel Clarimont/Broadway/Marisson/Cherry Loft 3* or Similar Hotel, Singapore\n•     02 Breakfast\n•     01 half day city tour\n\n<strong>Package Excludes :</strong>\n\n•     Visa Fees &amp; service charge per person BDT 4,000/-\n•     Lunch, Dinner\n•     Which is not mention in includes\n\n<strong>Hotel Information:</strong>\n\n<img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/70mmtours/images/in_hotel/broadway_hotel.jpg" alt="" width="164" height="109" />\n<table cellpadding="10px">\n<tbody>\n<tr valign="top">\n<td valign="top"><strong><span class="h5"><span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:_t228">Hotel Broadway / Similar</span></span></strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr valign="top">\n<td valign="top"><span class="h5">Star Rating:</span> <img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/staticResources/filled_star.jpg" alt="" width="18" height="18" /> <img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/staticResources/filled_star.jpg" alt="" width="18" height="18" /> <img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/staticResources/filled_star.jpg" alt="" width="18" height="18" /></td>\n</tr>\n<tr valign="top">\n<td valign="top">\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td valign="top"><span class="h5"> Address:</span></td>\n<td><span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt233:0:_t235" class="black_light1">Hotel Broadway</span><span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt233:0:_t238" class="black_light1">, Singapore</span><span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt233:0:_t239" class="black_light1">, Singapore</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr valign="top">\n<td valign="top"><span class="h5"> Hotel Description: </span>\n<span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:_t243" class="black_light1">There is a vast array of accommodation categories and types offered by several hotels here in Singapore that suit all the budgets and preferences within the country for your travel leisure and needs. These hotels range from the least budget and affordable hotels up to the most expensive, luxury and boutique-style five star hotels. If you will let yourself to surf the internet and search for the good fine deal hotels in Singapore that offers great discounts for your lodging and staying purposes in Singapore, precisely, this will be your great advantage to choose the best for you.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr valign="top">\n<td valign="top"><span class="h5">Features Characteristics:</span>\n• <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:0:_t247" class="black_light1">Bar/Lounge.</span>\n• <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:1:_t247" class="black_light1">Business Centre.</span>\n• <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:2:_t247" class="black_light1">Car parking.</span>\n• <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:3:_t247" class="black_light1">Doctor on call.</span>\n• <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:4:_t247" class="black_light1">Restaurant.</span>\n• <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:5:_t247" class="black_light1">Room service.</span>\n• <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:6:_t247" class="black_light1">Hot / cold water.</span><strong>About Destination:</strong><img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/70mmtours/images/int_destination/National_Orchid_Garden1.jpg" alt="" />\n\n<strong><span class="h5"><span id="one:j_idt311:1:j_idt313:5:_t317">National Orchid Garden, Singapore</span></span></strong>\n\n<span id="one:j_idt311:1:j_idt313:5:_t319" class="black_light1">The National Orchid Garden is located on the highest hill in the Singapore Botanic Gardens. Three hectares of carefully landscaped slopes provide a setting for over 1,000 species and 2,000 hybrids, with about 600 species and hybrids on display.</span>\n\n<img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/70mmtours/images/int_destination/little_india1.jpg" alt="" />\n\n<strong><span class="h5"><span id="one:j_idt311:1:j_idt313:6:_t317">Little India, Singapore</span></span></strong>\n\n<span id="one:j_idt311:1:j_idt313:6:_t319" class="black_light1">Little India is, as the name promises, the centre for the large Indian community in Singapore. While a rather sanitized version of the real thing, Little India retains its distinct identity without degenerating into a mere tourist attraction and is one of the most colourful and attractive places to visit in Singapore.</span>\n\n<img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/70mmtours/images/int_destination/sentosa1.jpg" alt="" />\n\n<strong><span class="h5"><span id="one:j_idt311:1:j_idt313:17:_t317">Sentosa Island</span></span></strong>\n\n<span id="one:j_idt311:1:j_idt313:17:_t319" class="black_light1">Most tourists visit Sentosa Island. Even locals like my family and myself pay a visit to Sentosa at least once a year. It''s definitely an ideal playground for people on family vacation. Plan for at least a day''s sightseeing in Sentosa.</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n&nbsp;', 'Singapore Tour (3 Days 2 Nights)', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '742-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-07-24 16:16:33', '2016-07-24 10:16:33', '', 742, 'http://ghuri.online/742-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
