(866, 1, '2016-08-09 23:12:42', '2016-08-09 17:12:42', '<span id="one:_t136" class="black_light1">Darjeeling is a City and a Municipality in the Indian state of West Bengal. It is located in the Mahabharat Range or Lesser Himalaya at an elevation of 7,100 ft (2,164.1 m). It is noted for its tea industry and the Darjeeling Himalayan Railway, a UNESCO World Heritage Site.</span>\r\n\r\n<strong>Package Includes :</strong>\r\n•     Return Air tickets with taxes of Biman (BG)\r\n•     Return AC Bus Ticket Up to Dhaka-Shiliguri-Dhaka.\r\n•     Sumo Jeep / tourist bus service up to Shiliguri-Darjeeling-Siliguri &amp; Sightseeing.\r\n•     02 Nights double sharing accommodation Hotel Sweet Home/Riddhi Siddhi Residency Hotel 3* or Similar Hotel\r\n•     01 full day sightseeing in Darjeeling\r\n\r\n<strong>Package Excludes :</strong>\r\n•     Visa fees, travel tax, Border expenses\r\n•     Lunch, Dinner\r\n•     Alcoholic beverages\r\n\r\n<strong>Hotel Information:</strong>\r\n\r\n<img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/images/riddhi_siddhi.jpg" alt="" width="177" height="100" />\r\n<table cellpadding="10px">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr valign="top">\r\n<td valign="top"><span class="h5"><span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:_t228">Riddhi Siddhi Residency Hotel / Similar</span></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr valign="top">\r\n<td valign="top"><span class="h5">Star Rating:</span> <img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/staticResources/filled_star.jpg" alt="" width="18" height="18" /> <img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/staticResources/filled_star.jpg" alt="" width="18" height="18" /> <img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/staticResources/filled_star.jpg" alt="" width="18" height="18" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr valign="top">\r\n<td valign="top">\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top"><span class="h5"> Address:</span></td>\r\n<td><span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt233:0:_t235" class="black_light1">Riddhi Siddhi Residency Hotel</span><span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt233:0:_t238" class="black_light1">, Darjeeling</span><span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt233:0:_t239" class="black_light1">, India</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr valign="top">\r\n<td valign="top"><span class="h5"> Hotel Description: </span>\r\n<span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:_t243" class="black_light1">Our resort is located in the center of all activities in Darjeeling. The attraction is not just the city, parks or sanctuary but the remarkably well preserved beautiful interior with some lovely landscapes. It is surrounded by the stretches of undulating span of tea estates with the panoramic grandeur of the Himalayas in the background of the resort. This was primarily developed with the intention to promote the enormous tourism resources and to encapsulate the spirit of the region. One can just stroll or drive around or take a hike around the region </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr valign="top">\r\n<td valign="top"><span class="h5">Features Characteristics:</span>\r\n• <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:0:_t247" class="black_light1">Bar/Lounge.</span>\r\n• <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:1:_t247" class="black_light1">Business Centre.</span>\r\n• <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:2:_t247" class="black_light1">Car parking.</span>\r\n• <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:3:_t247" class="black_light1">Doctor on call.</span>\r\n• <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:4:_t247" class="black_light1">Restaurant.</span>\r\n• <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:5:_t247" class="black_light1">Room service.</span>\r\n• <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:6:_t247" class="black_light1">Hot / cold water.</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<strong>About Destination:</strong>\r\n<table cellpadding="5px">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/70mmtours/images/4781/thumb.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n<td valign="top"><strong><span class="h5"><span id="one:j_idt311:1:j_idt313:5:_t317">Clock Tower</span></span></strong>\r\n\r\n<span id="one:j_idt311:1:j_idt313:5:_t319" class="black_light1">Clock Tower is one of the most happening places in town. This famous landmark of Darjeeling provides superb view of the valley below. Built by the Late Rai Sahib Kharga Bahadur Chettri who founded Darjeeling town.</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/70mmtours/images/4782/thumb.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n<td valign="top"><strong><span class="h5"><span id="one:j_idt311:1:j_idt313:6:_t317">Keventers</span></span></strong>\r\n\r\n<span id="one:j_idt311:1:j_idt313:6:_t319" class="black_light1">This place with it''s awesome western delicacies and cool view was featured in a number of movies and books. Don''t forget to try the chicken sausages and the chocolate milk shake</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/70mmtours/images/9015/thumb.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n<td valign="top"><strong><span class="h5"><span id="one:j_idt311:1:j_idt313:17:_t317">Japanese Temple</span></span></strong>\r\n\r\n<span id="one:j_idt311:1:j_idt313:17:_t319" class="black_light1">Japanese Temple, one of the most beautiful temples in Darjeeling, West Bengal state in India. Since it is located amidst a forest, this temple is very charming to see. The statues of two lions at the gate add more charm to the temple.</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<span id="one:j_idt311:1:j_idt313:5:_t319" class="black_light1"> </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Darjeeling Tour Package (03 Days 02 nights)', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'darjeeling-tour-package-03-days-02-nights', '', '', '2016-08-10 01:36:26', '2016-08-09 19:36:26', '', 0, 'http://ghuri.online/?post_type=tour&#038;p=866', 0, 'tour', '', 0),
