(916, 1, '2016-08-09 23:07:08', '2016-08-09 17:07:08', '<span id="one:_t136" class="black_light1">Kuala Lumpur is the capital of Malaysia. Kuala Lumpur has many interesting attractions; like Merdeka Square, Chinatown, Petronas Twin Towers and much more.\r\nGenting Resort presents a popular weekend getaway from the city heat, conveniently connected by the Karak Highway and major trunk roads, along with a cable car service from the satellite town of Gohtong Jaya</span>\r\n\r\n<strong>Package Includes :</strong>\r\n•     Return Air tickets with taxes by Malindo Air\r\n•     Airport-Hotel-Airport transfer (SIC)\r\n•     03 nights twin/triple accommodation at Kuala Lumpur Hotel Sentral Pudu, Sky Express &amp; Soleil 3* or Similar Hotel\r\n•     Full day Genting tour\r\n•     One way cable car ride\r\n\r\n<strong>Package Excludes :</strong>\r\n•     Visa Fees &amp; service charge per person BDT 6,500/-\r\n•     Lunch, Dinner\r\n•     Which is not mention in includes\r\n\r\n<strong>Hotel Information:</strong>\r\n\r\n<img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/70mmtours/images/in_hotel/arenaa_star.jpg" alt="" width="168" height="115" />\r\n<table cellpadding="10px">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr valign="top">\r\n<td valign="top"><strong><span class="h5"><span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:_t228">Hotel Sentral Pudu / Sky Express / Soleil or Similar</span></span></strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr valign="top">\r\n<td valign="top"><span class="h5">Star Rating:</span> <img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/staticResources/filled_star.jpg" alt="" width="18" height="18" /> <img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/staticResources/filled_star.jpg" alt="" width="18" height="18" /> <img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/staticResources/filled_star.jpg" alt="" width="18" height="18" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr valign="top">\r\n<td valign="top">\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top"><span class="h5">Address:</span></td>\r\n<td><span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt233:0:_t235" class="black_light1">Hotel Sentral Pudu</span><span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt233:0:_t238" class="black_light1">, Kuala Lampur</span><span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt233:0:_t239" class="black_light1">, Malaysia</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr valign="top">\r\n<td valign="top">&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span class="h5"><strong>Hotel Description:</strong> </span>\r\n<span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:_t243" class="black_light1">Strategically located in the heart of Kuala Lumpur, walking distance to the golden triangle, Bukit Bintang. Hotel Sentral Pudu offers a modern, stylish and comfortable stay in city. Step into the hotel and let the ultimate urban appeal of the hotel greets</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr valign="top">\r\n<td valign="top"><strong><span class="h5">Features Characteristics:</span> </strong>\r\n•      <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:0:_t247" class="black_light1">Bar/Lounge.</span>\r\n•      <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:1:_t247" class="black_light1">Business Centre.</span>\r\n•      <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:2:_t247" class="black_light1">Car parking.</span>\r\n•      <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:3:_t247" class="black_light1">Doctor on call.</span>\r\n•      <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:4:_t247" class="black_light1">Restaurant.</span>\r\n•      <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:5:_t247" class="black_light1">Room service.</span>\r\n•      <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:6:_t247" class="black_light1">Hot / cold water.</span><strong>About Destination:</strong>\r\n\r\n<img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/70mmtours/images/int_destination/amzing_park1.jpg" alt="" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Outdoor Amazing Park</strong>\r\n\r\nThe outdoor theme park is Genting Highland''s largest family attraction, offering recreational activities and amusement rides in a cooling environment high up the mountain slopes. Visitors can explore over 50 types of rides, including roller coasters, ferris wheels, swings, carousels, trains, cars and ships that tumble through the air, barrel down water channels or crawl slowly along a steel track.\r\n\r\n<img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/70mmtours/images/int_destination/genting_cable_cars1.jpg" alt="" />\r\n\r\n<strong><span class="h5"><span id="one:j_idt311:1:j_idt313:5:_t317">Genting Cable Cars Ride</span></span></strong>\r\n\r\n<span id="one:j_idt311:1:j_idt313:5:_t319" class="black_light1">Resorts World Genting may be located at a high altitude, but rest assured, it is actually easily accessible by various types of transportation. Have a leisure ride up to Resorts World Genting on the Skyway Cable Cars. They travel in a comfortable speed, allowing you to take in breathtaking views of nature at its best.</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', 'Kuala Lumpur & Gengting Tour', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'kuala-lumpur-gengting-tour', '', '', '2016-08-10 01:33:24', '2016-08-09 19:33:24', '', 0, 'http://ghuri.online/?post_type=tour&#038;p=916', 0, 'tour', '', 0),
