(919, 1, '2016-08-02 17:21:42', '2016-08-02 11:21:42', '<span id="one:_t136" class="black_light1">Phuket is one of the southern provinces (changwat) of Thailand. It consists of the island of Phuket, the country''s largest island, and another 32 smaller islands off its coast. It lies off the west coast of Thailand in the Andaman Sea.</span>\n\n<strong>Package Includes :</strong>\n•     Return Air Tickets for by Regent Air + Air Asia with all taxes.\n•     Airport-Hotel-Airport transfer both cities (SIC)\n•     02 nights double sharing accommodation at APK Resort 3* or Similar Hotel, Phuket\n•     02 nights double sharing accommodation at Hotel Ambassador/Unico Express Hotel 3* or Similar Hotel, Bangkok\n\n<strong>Package Excludes :</strong>\n•     Visa Fees &amp; service charge per person BDT 4,500/-\n•     Lunch, Dinner\n•     Which is not mention in includes\n\n<strong>Hotel Information:</strong>\n\n<img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/70mmtours/images/in_hotel/apk.jpg" alt="" width="154" height="100" />\n<table cellpadding="10px">\n<tbody>\n<tr valign="top">\n<td valign="top"><span class="h5"><span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:_t228">Hotel APK Resort / Similar</span></span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr valign="top">\n<td valign="top"><span class="h5">Star Rating:</span> <img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/staticResources/filled_star.jpg" alt="" width="18" height="18" /> <img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/staticResources/filled_star.jpg" alt="" width="18" height="18" /> <img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/staticResources/filled_star.jpg" alt="" width="18" height="18" /></td>\n</tr>\n<tr valign="top">\n<td valign="top">\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td valign="top"><span class="h5"> Address:</span></td>\n<td><span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt233:0:_t235" class="black_light1">Hotel APK Resort</span><span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt233:0:_t238" class="black_light1">, Phuket</span><span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt233:0:_t239" class="black_light1">, Thailand</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr valign="top">\n<td valign="top"><span class="h5"> Hotel Description: </span>\n<span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:_t243" class="black_light1">THE AMBASSADOR HOTEL BANGKOK 171 Soi 11, Sukhumvit Road., Bangkok 10110,Thailand(close to Nana Skytrain Station) The Ambassador Hotel Bangkok : Is situated at a prime spot in the heart of fashionable Sukhumvit Rd., Bangkok''s legendary commercial district. Half an hour from Bangkok''s Don Muang Internation Airport, close to Queen Sirikit National Convention Centre, and near great shopping and entertainment venues, the Ambassdor is only two minutes walk from Nana Skytrain Station.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr valign="top">\n<td valign="top"><span class="h5">Features Characteristics:</span>\n• <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:0:_t247" class="black_light1">Bar/Lounge.</span>\n• <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:1:_t247" class="black_light1">Business Centre.</span>\n• <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:2:_t247" class="black_light1">Car parking.</span>\n• <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:3:_t247" class="black_light1">Doctor on call.</span>\n• <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:4:_t247" class="black_light1">Restaurant.</span>\n• <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:5:_t247" class="black_light1">Room service.</span>\n• <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:6:_t247" class="black_light1">Hot / cold water.</span><strong>About Destination:</strong>\n\n<img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/70mmtours/images/int_destination/james_bond1.jpg" alt="" />\n\n<strong><span class="h5"><span id="one:j_idt311:1:j_idt313:5:_t317">James Bond Island Phuket</span></span></strong>\n\n<span id="one:j_idt311:1:j_idt313:5:_t319" class="black_light1">James Bond Island in Phang Nga Bay Attractions Nearby PhuketJames Bond Island is a famous landmark in Phang Nga Bay. It first found its way onto the international tourist map through its starring role in the James Bond movie ''The Man with the Golden Gun''. A distinctive feature of this famous bay is the number of sheer limestone cliffs that vertically jut out of the emerald-green water.</span>\n\n<img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/70mmtours/images/int_destination/phi_phi1.jpg" alt="" />\n\n<strong>Phi Phi Island</strong>\n\nThe Phi Phi islands are some of the loveliest in Southeast Asia. Just a 45-minute speedboat jaunt and a 90-minute ferryboat ride from Phuket, these picture postcard islands offer the ultimate tropical getaway.Classic beaches, stunning rock formations, and vivid turquoise waters teeming with colourful marine life - it''s paradise perfected.\n\n<img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/70mmtours/images/int_destination/bangla_road1.jpg" alt="" />\n\n<strong><span class="h5"><span id="one:j_idt311:1:j_idt313:17:_t317">Bangla Road Phuket</span></span></strong>\n\n<span id="one:j_idt311:1:j_idt313:17:_t319" class="black_light1">Bangla Road only really comes to life when the sun sets. The road is closed to vehicle traffic and becomes 400 metres of neon lights, loud music, cheap beer and sexy girls. Jammed most nights of the year, it is actually totally unthreatening and is a lively place to walk around as bars compete for customers.</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>', 'Bangkok & Phuket Tour Package ( 05 Days 04 Nights )', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '864-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-08-02 17:21:42', '2016-08-02 11:21:42', '', 864, 'http://ghuri.online/864-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(920, 1, '2016-08-02 17:22:26', '2016-08-02 11:22:26', '<span id="one:_t136" class="black_light1">Pattaya City is a self-governing municipal area which covers the whole tambon Nong Prue and Na Kluea and parts of Huai Yai and Nong Pla Lai. The city is in the heavily industrial Eastern Seaboard zone, along with Si Racha, Laem Chabang, and Chonburi. It has a population exceeding 100,000 (2007). Pattaya is the centre of the Pattaya-Chonburi Metropolitan Area - the conurbation in Chonburi Province - with a total population exceeding 1,000,000.</span>\n\n<strong>Package Includes :</strong>\n•     Return Air tickets by Regent Air with Taxes\n•     Airport-Pattaya Hotel–Bangkok Hotel-Airport transfer both cities\n•     01 night double sharing accommodation at Hotel The Seasons or Beverly Plaza 3* or Similar Hotel, Pattaya\n•     02 nights double sharing accommodation at Hotel Ambassador or Unico Express Hotel 3* or Similar Hotel, Bangkok\n\n<strong>Package Excludes :</strong>\n•     Visa Fees &amp; service charge per person BDT 4,500/-\n•     Lunch, Dinner\n•     Which is not mention in includes\n\n<strong>Hotel Information:</strong>\n\n<img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/70mmtours/images/in_hotel/seasons_hotel.jpg" alt="" width="162" height="107" />\n<table cellpadding="10px">\n<tbody>\n<tr valign="top">\n<td valign="top"><span class="h5"><span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:_t228">Hotel The Seasons / Similar</span></span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr valign="top">\n<td valign="top"><span class="h5">Star Rating:</span> <img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/staticResources/filled_star.jpg" alt="" width="18" height="18" /> <img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/staticResources/filled_star.jpg" alt="" width="18" height="18" /> <img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/staticResources/filled_star.jpg" alt="" width="18" height="18" /></td>\n</tr>\n<tr valign="top">\n<td valign="top">\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td valign="top"><span class="h5"> Address:</span></td>\n<td><span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt233:0:_t235" class="black_light1">Hotel The Seasons</span><span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt233:0:_t238" class="black_light1">, Pattaya</span><span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt233:0:_t239" class="black_light1">, Thailand</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr valign="top">\n<td valign="top"><span class="h5"> Hotel Description: </span>\n<span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:_t243" class="black_light1">The Seasons Bangkok Huamark is an economy hotel located in Ramkamhaeng area, giving you comfort and style and exemplary service. We welcome you with a smile 24 hours and assure you of quality and convenience with professional hospitality staff members. The Seasons Bangkok Huamark offers casual dining, flexible breakfast options, 24-hours room service, meeting facilities, and covered car parking. Come and stay with us and really enjoy your holiday.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr valign="top">\n<td valign="top"><span class="h5">Features Characteristics:</span>\n• <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:0:_t247" class="black_light1">Bar/Lounge.</span>\n• <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:1:_t247" class="black_light1">Business Centre.</span>\n• <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:2:_t247" class="black_light1">Car parking.</span>\n• <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:3:_t247" class="black_light1">Doctor on call.</span>\n• <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:4:_t247" class="black_light1">Restaurant.</span>\n• <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:5:_t247" class="black_light1">Room service.</span>\n• <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:6:_t247" class="black_light1">Hot / cold water.</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong>About Destination:</strong>\n\n<img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/70mmtours/images/int_destination/pattaya1.jpg" alt="" />\n\n<strong><span class="h5"><span id="one:j_idt311:1:j_idt313:5:_t317">Coral Island</span></span></strong>\n\n<span id="one:j_idt311:1:j_idt313:5:_t319" class="black_light1">The beautiful beaches of Koh Larn-an idyllic island located just west of Pattaya – make a perfect day trip to visit Coral Island by speed boat – Coral formations and the beautiful underwater life , Take this opportunity to enjoy the various water Sports activities like Parachute , Water Scooter, Banana boat , Under sea walk etc</span>\n\n<img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/70mmtours/images/int_destination/alcazar_show1.jpg" alt="" />\n\n<strong><span class="h5"><span id="one:j_idt311:1:j_idt313:6:_t317">Alcazar Show</span></span></strong>\n\n<span id="one:j_idt311:1:j_idt313:6:_t319" class="black_light1">Pattaya has made good of its long-time love affair with ladyboys. Extravagant costumes, convincingly stunning ladyboys, spectacular stage sets are all part of a grander show that delights you with non-stop fantasmic entertainment, from the Russian stage to K-Pop to Persian harlem and even outer space</span>\n\n<img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/70mmtours/images/int_destination/walking1.jpg" alt="" />\n\n<strong><span class="h5"><span id="one:j_idt311:1:j_idt313:17:_t317">Walking Street, Pattaya</span></span></strong>\n\n<span id="one:j_idt311:1:j_idt313:17:_t319" class="black_light1">It is a tourist attraction that draws foreigners and Thai nationals, primarily for the night life. The area includes seafood restaurants, live music venues, beer bars, discothèques, sports bars, go-go bars, and nightclubs</span>', 'Bangkok & Pattaya Tour Package ( 04 Days 03 Nights )', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '861-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-08-02 17:22:26', '2016-08-02 11:22:26', '', 861, 'http://ghuri.online/861-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(921, 1, '2016-08-02 17:45:05', '2016-08-02 11:45:05', '<span id="one:_t136" class="black_light1">Singapore is a modern city-state and island country in Southeast Asia. It lies off the southern tip of the Malay Peninsula and is 137 kilometres (85 mi) north of the equator.\r\nKuala Lumpur is the capital of Malaysia. Over 8 million people live within the greater Kuala Lumpur area which is clearly noticeable by the huge and vast amounts of traffic that goes into the city every morning, and slowly leaves the city in the evening.</span>\r\n\r\n<strong>Package Includes :</strong>\r\n•     Dhaka-Singapore Air tickets by Tiger Airways with all taxes.\r\n•     Kuala Lumpur-Dhaka Air tickets by Malindo Air with all taxes.\r\n•     Singapore-Kuala Lumpur by AC Bus.\r\n•     02 Nights double sharing stay at Hotel Clarimont / Broadway / Marisson / Cherry Left 3* or Similar Hotel at Singapore.\r\n\r\n<strong>Package Excludes :</strong>\r\n•     Visa fees &amp; service charge for two countries per person BDT 10,000/-\r\n•     Lunch, Dinner\r\n•     Which is not mention in includes\r\n\r\n<strong>Hotel Information:</strong>\r\n\r\n<img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/70mmtours/images/in_hotel/broadway_hotel.jpg" alt="" width="160" height="105" />\r\n<table cellpadding="10px">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr valign="top">\r\n<td valign="top"><strong><span class="h5"><span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:_t228">Hotel Broadway / Similar</span></span></strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr valign="top">\r\n<td valign="top"><span class="h5">Star Rating:</span> <img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/staticResources/filled_star.jpg" alt="" width="18" height="18" /> <img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/staticResources/filled_star.jpg" alt="" width="18" height="18" /> <img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/staticResources/filled_star.jpg" alt="" width="18" height="18" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr valign="top">\r\n<td valign="top">\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top"><span class="h5"> Address:</span></td>\r\n<td><span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt233:0:_t235" class="black_light1">Hotel Broadway</span><span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt233:0:_t238" class="black_light1">, Singapore</span><span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt233:0:_t239" class="black_light1">, Singapore</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr valign="top">\r\n<td valign="top"><strong><span class="h5"> Hotel Description: </span></strong>\r\n<span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:_t243" class="black_light1">There is a vast array of accommodation categories and types offered by several hotels here in Singapore that suit all the budgets and preferences within the country for your travel leisure and needs. These hotels range from the least budget and affordable hotels up to the most expensive, luxury and boutique-style five star hotels. If you will let yourself to surf the internet and search for the good fine deal hotels in Singapore that offers great discounts for your lodging and staying purposes in Singapore, precisely, this will be your great advantage to choose the best for you.</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr valign="top">\r\n<td valign="top"><span class="h5">Features Characteristics:</span>\r\n• <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:0:_t247" class="black_light1">Bar/Lounge.</span>\r\n• <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:1:_t247" class="black_light1">Business Centre.</span>\r\n• <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:2:_t247" class="black_light1">Car parking.</span>\r\n• <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:3:_t247" class="black_light1">Doctor on call.</span>\r\n• <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:4:_t247" class="black_light1">Restaurant.</span>\r\n• <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:5:_t247" class="black_light1">Room service.</span>\r\n• <span id="one:j_idt221:0:j_idt223:1:j_idt245:6:_t247" class="black_light1">Hot / cold water.</span>&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>About Destination:</strong>\r\n\r\n<img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/70mmtours/images/int_destination/National_Orchid_Garden1.jpg" alt="" />\r\n\r\n<strong>National Orchid Garden, Singapore</strong>\r\n\r\nThe National Orchid Garden is located on the highest hill in the Singapore Botanic Gardens. Three hectares of carefully landscaped slopes provide a setting for over 1,000 species and 2,000 hybrids, with about 600 species and hybrids on display.\r\n\r\n<img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/70mmtours/images/int_destination/little_india1.jpg" alt="" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Little India, Singapore</strong>\r\n\r\nLittle India is, as the name promises, the centre for the large Indian community in Singapore. While a rather sanitized version of the real thing, Little India retains its distinct identity without degenerating into a mere tourist attraction and is one of the most colourful and attractive places to visit in Singapore.\r\n\r\n<img src="http://www.bd-tours.com/s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/70mmtours/images/int_destination/tower4.jpg" alt="" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Petronas Towers</strong>\r\n\r\nThe Petronas Towers are an impressive icon of Kuala Lumpur. They are visable from just about everywhere in the city, and dominate the night sky.1,000 tickets are issued per day for the tour of the Skybridge. The tickets are free and on a first come first served basis.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', 'Singapore & Kuala Lumpur Tour', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'singapore-kuala-lumpur-tour', '', '', '2016-08-02 17:45:45', '2016-08-02 11:45:45', '', 0, 'http://ghuri.online/?post_type=tour&#038;p=921', 0, 'tour', '', 0),
