(43, 'Grand Sultan Tea Resort & Golf', NULL, 'About Grand Sultan Tea Resort & Golf Grand Sultan Tea Resort & Golf, a Wonder in the surrounding of lavishing greenery of Srimongal (the Tea Capital of Bangladesh). Equipped with all modern state of art Amenities and Facilities, Located within an area of 13.02 acres, this Resort is the true combination of Ultimate Luxury, Gracious Hospitality and Admirable Greenery. Classified in 07 categories, GS welcomes you with 135 Rooms and Suites to meet all your Expectations.', 'ddf52bdb6cbd16d56f683274b6feaa47.jpg', 'Sylhet', NULL, '2016-02-06 21:43:39', 23300, 1, ' Radhanagar, Sreemongal, Moulvibazar, Sylhet, Bangladesh.', '24.904539', '91.8611011', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, 0, 1, NULL, 'Cancellation Policy: One night room charge will be applicable for Non arrivals/Cancellation unless hotel received cancellation notice in writing 72 hours prior to the hotel check in time by the guest or the organization concerned. Children Policy: Children aged from 0-6 years will not be charged for the stay in the room. Children under 7-12 years may be accommodated in the same room as parents at no extra cost but breakfast included. Extra Bed Policy:  Any additional children or adults are charged on per night 3200 Taka for extra beds. The maximum number of extra beds in a room is 1. Any type of extra bed is upon request and needs to be confirmed by management. Additional fees are not calculated automatically in the total cost and will have to be paid for separately during your stay.     Pets Policy: Petrs are Not allowed Prepayment Policy: Prepayment is possible when guest inform us to cancel his/her booking then we return booking amount within 48 or 72 hours in time.', 'Property highlights: Tea Garden, Golf, Largest Bankquet. Check in time: 2:00 PM Check out time: 12:00 PM Early check in time: 6:00 AM Late check out time: 6:00PM Tagline: Enjoy your elegant moment with luxury. Establishment year: 2010 Payment method: AMEX,VISA,MasterCard Currencies: