(44, 'Britannia Hotel', NULL, 'About Britannia Hotel Welcome to Britannia Hotel, located Ambarkhana, Sylhet and established in 16th December 2009. It offers 69 rooms with all modern amenities of international standard. Britannia Hotel has well equipped rooms for board meeting, conference, retreat etc. It is the home for trees and plants of four hundred varieties. Many extinct plants thrive here is highest attraction to be enjoyed by any nature lover.Air Conditioned Room TheBrassarie Restaurant Conference and Banquet Facility Attached bathroom Daily Toiletries Amenities 24 Hour Front Desk Staff Basement Parking Wifi Internet from Room', 'b8756f27360d5967c2d5d239485e0565.jpg', 'Sylhet', NULL, '2016-02-06 21:43:45', 2160, 1, ' Britannia Hotel B-95 Waves, Shahjalal Road, Ambarkhana, Sylhet-3100', '24.904539', '91.8611011', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, 0, 1, NULL, 'Cancellation Policy: One night room charge will be applicable for Non arrivals/Cancellation unless hotel received cancellation notice in writing 48 hours prior to the hotel check in time by the guest or the organization concerned. Children Policy: All children are welcome. Extra Bed Policy: No Extra Bed Available.     Pets Policy: Pets are not allowed. Prepayment Policy: Prepayment is possible when guest inform us to cancel his/her booking then we return booking amount within 48 or 72 hours in time.', 'Property highlights: Free! WiFi is available in all areas and is free of charge.  Check in time: 14 : 00 – 23 : 00 Hours Check out time: 00 – 11 :00 Hours 00 – 11 :00 Hours 00 – 11 :00 Hours Early check in time: Late check out time: Tagline: Once is not enough Establishment year: 2009 Payment method: AMEX,VISA,MasterCard Currencies: BDT'),
(45, 'Hotel Metro International', NULL, 'About Hotel Metro International To Enjoy one of the most memorable holiday of your life time with great fun & lovely food. We at Hotel Metro International take every possible effort to make our Guests not only meet but to exceed their expectations. All our hospitality establishments provide only the highest levels of comfortable quality accommodations and conference facilities and we are the perfect choice for your next city break, business meeting or special family occasion.Hotel Metro International Is A New Luxury Magnificent Business Class Hotel Ideally Located In The Heart Of Sylhet City Centre Hotel Metro International Provides Many First Class Services, Facilities And Hospitality At Rates Guests Like You Would Find Convenient. Hotel Metro International Aims To Provide Customers With An Excellent And Truly Memorable Experience. Our Room Rates Are Unrivalled By any Other International Standard Hotel in the Country without Compromising On Quality. Hotel Metro International Both Business And Leisure Travelers Will Enjoy All That An International Three Star Standard Hotel Can Offer From First Class Surroundings To World Class Hospitality, All In the Metro Style. Rooms are with private baths, mini bar, TV with 60 cable channel & Internet connection. Suite is also with one or two bed room with separate sitting room      ', '3a65c7f75c7b43f81912499e82e02683.jpg', 'Sylhet', NULL, '2016-02-06 21:43:49', 2750, 1, ' Dhupadighir Per (south),East Bondor Bazar,Sylhet-3100 Bangladesh', '24.904539', '91.8611011', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, 0, 1, NULL, 'Cancellation Policy: One night room charge will be applicable for Non arrivals/Cancellation unless hotel received cancellation notice in writing 48 hours prior to the hotel check in time by the guest or the organization concerned. Children Policy: Children can be accommodated with parents. Extra Bed Policy: Any additional children or adults are charged for per night 1200 Taka for extra beds. Th