(46, 'Hotel Garden Inn', NULL, 'About Hotel Garden Inn A team of professionals having background of 3 star Hotel at home and abroad remain standby for your service as per your need. Hotel Garden Inn is a world class business hotel located in the bankof the river Surma, Upashahor, Sylhet. It is a walking distance from most of the foreign missions like british Visa processing Center, 30 Minutes drive from Osmani International airport, 10 Minutes drive from HajratShahjalal (R) Majar and very closed to Garden City Shopping Complex. Hotel Garden Inn restaurant offers you the finest Chinese/Bangladeshi/Continental/Thai dishes, along with especially good value. From the moment you step inside, you’ll find the welcome is warm and authentically delicious    ', '812988079fd321ec70d51e1c6cc6a8cc.jpg', 'Sylhet', NULL, '2016-02-06 21:43:54', 2880, 1, ' Garden Tower, Shah Jalal Bridge link Road, Sylhet', '24.904539', '91.8611011', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, 0, 1, NULL, 'Cancellation Policy: One night room charge will be applicable for Non arrivals/Cancellation unless hotel received cancellation notice in writing 48 hours prior to the hotel check in time by the guest or the organization concerned. Children Policy: Pets are not allowed. Extra Bed Policy: Any additional children or adults are charged on per night 500 Taka for extra beds. The maximum number of extra beds in a room is 1. Any type of extra bed is upon request and needs to be confirmed by management. Additional fees are not calculated automatically in the total cost and will have to be paid for separately during your stay. Pets Policy: Pets are not allowed. Prepayment Policy: Prepayment is possible when guest inform us to cancel his/her booking then we return booking amount within 48 or 72 hours in time.', 'Property highlights: Fee wi-fi, Free Parking Check in time: From 12:00 Check out time: Until 12:00 Early check in time: Late check out time: Tagline: An exclusive name in comfort and relax Establishment year: Payment metho