(47, 'Lemon Garden Resort', NULL, 'About Lemon Garden Resort Lemon Garden Resort is situated at 4 kilometer away from Sreemangal town.The area is named as Lawachara. One gets panoramic views of mountains,Lemon Garden,hills and forests stretching hilly area with the amazing view green forests, blue skies and cloud-adorned mountains all come together. As far as ones eyes can see. Considering that Garden, one of the highest rainfall areas of the Country.', '9b81dd835bffb9a98d3c65c185e412e5.JPG', 'Sylhet', NULL, '2016-02-06 21:44:02', 5000, 1, ' Lawachara Sreimangal, 3210 Moulvi Bazar, Sylhet, Bangladesh', '24.904539', '91.8611011', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, 0, 1, NULL, 'Cancellation Policy: One night room charge will be applicable for Non arrivals/Cancellation unless hotel received cancellation notice in writing 48 hours prior to the hotel check in time by the guest or the organization concerned. Children Policy: Children can be accommodated with parents. Any one child age of 12 or below they can stay with parents but breakfast will be charged. No more than one child can stay in a room. Child age must be confirmed in online booking or by phone. If child is found to be of higher age then declared at booking time then extra bed charge will be charged. Extra Bed Policy:   No Extra Bed Available     ed are not available Pets Policy: Pets are not allowed. Prepayment Policy: Prepayment is possible when guest inform us 72 hours prior to the hotel check in time. ', 'Property highlights: Free parking   Check in time: 11 : 00 AM Check out time: 12: 00 PM Early check in time: Late check out time: Tagline: We Like To keep it that Way Establishment year: Payment method: VISA,MasterCard Currencies: BDT'),
(48, 'Hotel Fortune Garden', NULL, 'About Hotel Fortune Garden Welcome to the Magnificent Hotel Fortune Garden, a Modern new exclusive Hotel in the heart of Sylhet, a city with a holy shrine, greenery tea garden, wonderful water fall and lots of cultural activities, it makes one of the most attractive tourist cities in Bangladesh. With state-of-the art foreign interior and all other facilities, its makes our hotel most modern equipped in the city. By focusing on combining unparalleled levels of service with class-leading facilities, the Fortune Garden aims to provide customers with a unique and truly memorable experience. In addition, we will bring extraordinary value to the fast growing hospitality sector. The hotel room rates will be similar standard within other hotels without compromising on quality.    ', '26301003c4a850bc25eab697e82b4ffa.jpg', 'Sylhet', NULL, '2016-02-06 21:44:06', 2750, 1, ' Hotel Fortune Garden 29/A, Bongobir Road, Dhaka - Sylhet Highway, Sylhet-3100, Bangladesh', '24.904539', '91.8611011', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, 0, 1, NULL, 'Cancellation Policy: One night room charge will be applicable for Non arrivals/Cancellation unless hotel received cancellation notice in writing 48 hours prior to the hotel check in time by the guest or the organization concerned. Children Policy: Children aged from 0-6 years will not be charged for the stay in the room. Children under 7-12 years may be accommodated in the same room as parents at no extra cost but breakfast included.                                                                      Extra Bed Policy: Any additional children or adults are charged on per night 500 Taka for extra beds. The maximum number of extra beds in a room is 1. Any type of extra bed is upon request and needs to be confirmed by management. Additional fees are not calculated automatically in the total cost and will have to be paid for separately during your stay.       Pets Policy: Pets are not allowed. Prepayment Policy: The prepaymen