(49, 'Rain forest Resort', NULL, 'About Rain forest Resort Sreemongal- the Tea capital of Bangladesh is just 191km from Dhaka. The lush green tea plantation, Rubber garden and the beautiful lake always attract the foreign tourists. The Lauawachara rain forest is the habitat of white browed Gibbons,hornbills and many other rare animals and birds. You will be inspired to visit the colorful Manipuri tribal culture. Explore also Khashia and Tripra life style. The Madhobkhunda waterfall and the stone query from the hilly river at Jaflong (Bangladesh - India border) will be interesting for anyone. Sreemongal is also famous for lemon, pineapple, orange and many other delicious fruits. The rain forest and wetlands of Sreemongal and Sylhet are the best place for bird watching. Here you may find many species of local and migratory birds.', '5a5a2a48731ab66fd6839dd1d320bf60.jpg', 'Sylhet', NULL, '2016-02-06 21:44:09', 2500, 1, ' Uttarsure, Hobigang Road, Sreemangal, Moulabi Bazar.', '24.904539', '91.8611011', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, 0, 1, NULL, 'Cancellation Policy: One night room charge will be applicable for Non arrivals/Cancellation unless hotel received cancellation notice in writing 7 days prior to the hotel check in time by the guest or the organization concerned. Children Policy: Children can be accommodated with parents.   Extra Bed Policy: Any additional children or adults are charged on per night for extra beds. The maximum number of extra beds in a room is 1. Any type of extra bed is upon request and needs to be confirmed by management. Additional fees are not calculated automatically in the total cost and will have to be paid for separately during your stay.       Pets Policy: Pets are not allowed. Prepayment Policy: Prepayment is possible when guest inform us to cancel his/her booking then we return booking amount within 7 days in time.', 'Property highlights: Free Wifi, Free Parking Check in time: From : 12 :00 PM Check out time: Until : 12: 00 AM Early check in time: Late check out time: Tagline: Establishment year: Payment method: VISA,MasterCard Currencies: BDT'),
(50, 'Almas Hotel Sylhet', NULL, 'About Almas Hotel Sylhet Almas Hotel Sylhet. Almas hotel is established in sylhet to provide best facilities. We are committed to serve throughout the nation and international. We are very close to the city, only 2 minutes distance from Shahporan Mazar. Almas Hotel is a truly iconic hotel, offering something special for everyone. Standing tall as a beacon of grandeur and refinement among vacation resort destinations, this luxury Almas hotel will offer you and your family a legendary getaway.', '2cefec0c0e41169b7b9a758642d1ac11.jpg', 'Sylhet', NULL, '2016-02-06 21:44:14', 1875, 1, ' House No:1, Majar Gate, Shahparan,Sylhet Bangladesh..', '24.904539', '91.8611011', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, 0, 1, NULL, 'Cancellation Policy: One night room charge will be applicable for Non arrivals/Cancellation unless hotel received cancellation notice in writing 48 hours prior to the hotel check in time by the guest or the organization concerned.   Children Policy: Children can be accommodated with parents.                                      Extra Bed Policy: Any additional children or adults are charged on per night 700 Taka for extra beds. The maximum number of extra beds in a room is 1. Any type of extra bed is upon request and needs to be confirmed by management. Additional fees are not calculated automatically in the total cost and will have to be paid for separately during your stay. Pets Policy: Pets are not allowed.                                              Prepayment Policy: Prepayment is possible when guest inform us to cancel his/her booking then we return booking amount within 48 or 72 hours in time.', 'Property highlights: free WIFi, Free parking Check in time: 12:00PM Check out time: 12:00PM Early check in time: 10:00AM Late check out time: 12:00PM Tagline: A Touch of Resort at an affordable Price Establishment year: 2015 Payment method: AMEX,VISA,MasterCard Currencies: USD,BDT'),
(51, 'DuSai Resort & Spa', NULL, 'About DuSai Resort & Spa DuSai Resort & Spa is the first luxurious 5 star standard boutique Villa Resort & Spa nestled within a small tropical forest on hillocks dotted with thousands of trees and flanked by a 1000 feet long serpentine lake in the south and a reserved forest area in the north side, just beside the largest concentration of tea gardens in Moulvibazar about 200 kms north-east of Dhaka. We are... • A perfect place for nature lovers looking for quite tranquility. • A place of choice for couples and families. • A secret and enchanting hideaway for honeymooners. • An adventurous destination to explore the charms of the tea gardens, the largest rain forest and the newly discovered 160 ft. high three layered Ham Ham waterfall. • A preferred destination for small corporate meetings and conferences.', '26d5db048eb11739b197f2fd64ec71c6.jpg', 'Sylhet', NULL, '2016-02-06 21:44:23', 12144, 1, ' Niteshwar, Giashnagar,, Sadar Sub-District Moulvibazar - 3200 Bangladesh', '24.904539', '91.8611011', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, 0, 1, NULL, 'Cancellation Policy: Peak Season (December-January): 1. 10 days or more : No Charge. 2. Between 9-7 days : 50% of booking value. 3. Less then 7 days or no shows : Full duration of Booking will be charged. Regular Season (All Months except Above): 1. Cancellation 7 Days or more - No charge. 2. Less then 7 days but more then 3 days - First night room charge 3. 3 days or less - Full booking charge. Children Policy: All Children Are Welcome .                                                                         Extra Bed Policy: Any additional children or adults are charged for night for extra beds. The maximum number of extra beds in a room is 1. Any type of extra bed is upon request and needs to be confirmed by management. Additional fees are not calculated automatically in the total cost and will have to be paid for separately during your stay.         Pets Policy: Pets are not allowed. Prepayment Policy: Prepayment is depend on booking date. ', 'Property highlights: Free WiFi & Free Parking  Check in time: 12:00 PM Check out time: 12 :00 PM Early check in time: 11:00 AM Late check out time: 12:30 PM Tagline: First luxurious 5 star standard boutique Villa Resort & Spa Establishment year: Payment method: AMEX,VISA,MasterCard Currencies: BDT'),
(52, 'Hotel Hill View', NULL, 'About Hotel Hill View Hotel Hill View is situated at Bus Stand, Bandarban Main Road, Chittagong, Bangladesh. There are VIP Suite, Royal Suite, Super Deluxe, Deluxe, Couple + Couple, Couple + Single and Couple/Single room facilities in this hotel. There are AC and Non AC rooms are available in this Hotel. They have a well-decorated conference room with the capacity of over 100 people. Hotel Hill View has their own Restaurant. They provide delicious dishes with Chinese, Thai and Bengali food items at reasonable price. They offer special discount in off season for non AC rooms and group booking for long stay.', '9ba3bb231eb7864c4662f6e18247834e.jpg', 'Bandarban', NULL, '2016-02-06 21:55:19', 1380, 1, ' Bus Stand, Bandarban Main Road, Chittagong', '22.1935628', '92.2187476', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, 0, 1, NULL, 'Cancellation Policy: One night room charge will be applicable for Non arrivals/Cancellation unless hotel received cancellation notice in writing 72 hours prior to the hotel check in time by the guest or the organization concerned. Children Policy: All Children Are Welcome .                                                                         Extra Bed Policy: Any additional children or adults are charged for night for extra beds. The maximum number of extra beds in a room is 1. Any type of extra bed is upon request and needs to be confirmed by management. Additional fees are not calculated automatically in the total cost and will have to be paid for separately during your stay.         Pets Policy: Pets are not allowed. Prepayment Policy: Prepayment is possible when guest inform us 48 hours prior to the hotel check in time. ', 'Property highlights: Free Parking  Check in time: 12:00PM Check out time: 12:00 PM Early check in time: 11:00 AM Late check out time: 2:00 PM Tagline: Establishment year: 2001 Payment method: Currencies: BDT'),
(53, 'Hillside Resort', NULL, 'About Hillside Resort In 2001, we have built the "Hillside Resort" in Bandarban, which is unique in all respects. We are very proud to say that within this very short period of time it has become a very popular place for both local foreign tourists. This is in fact the only one of its kind in the country and a perfect place for your retreat. At present with different categories of rooms, we can accommodate 40-50 people at this resort. Our resort is only 2 hours drive away from Chittagong. In the attached restaurant named “Restora Riggre Khyang” varieties of local and international cuisine are available. Options are there for trekking and sightseeing, and, best of all, tribal cottages with an incomparable view of the Sangu River flowing through the valley below.', '39c3a7885863354a8ee56a04aca938f9.jpg', 'Bandarban', NULL, '2016-02-06 21:55:26', 900, 1, ' Milonchhori Chimbuk Road, Bandarban.', '22.1935628', '92.2187476', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, 0, 1, NULL, 'Cancellation Policy: One night room charge will be applicable for Non arrivals/Cancellation unless hotel received cancellation notice in writing 48 hours prior to the hotel check in time by the guest or the organization concerned. Children Policy: All children  are allowed                                                               Extra Bed Policy: Any additional children or adults are charged 1000 tk for  extra beds. The maximum number of extra beds in a room is 1. Any type of extra bed is upon request and needs to be confirmed by management. Additional fees are not calculated automatically in the total cost and will have to be paid for separately during your stay.     Pets Policy: Pets are not allowed. Prepayment Policy: Prepayment is possible when guest inform us 48 hours prior to thehotel check in time. ', 'Property highlights: Free WiFi & Free Parking  Check in time: 12:00 pm Check out time: 10:00AM Early check in time: 10:AM Late check out time: Check out within 4 hours after th